testcase.name: sorting single module should return list with that module
sortByTotalLength should handle modules with different lengths
sorting empty repository should return empty list
sortByContent should sort modules by content
sorting should not modify the original repository
sortByTotalLength should sort by title + content length
sortByTitle should sort modules by title
sortByContentLength should sort by content length
sortByTitleLength with same length should sort by title
sortByContent should handle cyrillic and latin characters
sortByTitleLength should sort by title length
